r12344 | massiot | 2005-08-22 19:58:20 +0200 (Mon, 22 Aug 2005) | 8 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/include/vlc_common.h
   M /trunk/include/vlc_symbols.h
   M /trunk/modules/control/http/http.c
