r10478 | fenrir | 2005-03-29 18:01:23 +0200 (Tue, 29 Mar 2005) | 8 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/include/configuration.h
   M /trunk/include/vlc_access.h
   M /trunk/include/vlc_config_cat.h
